Description: Manage ROS workspaces with multiple Gitlab repositories (Python 3)
 rosrepo is the standard tool for ROS workspace management in Fraunhofer
 FKIE with a number of nice features:
 .
  - More comfortable management of package builds and dependencies
  - Mark packages as pinned so they will always be built
  - Clone, push, and pull from Gitlab repositories
  - Automatically clone Gitlab projects to satisfy package dependencies
 .
 This package provides the Python 3 version of rosrepo.

